rst and finding nothing but dead ends, i quickly realized that my health bar was quickly reaching 30 percent. Not one to give in but knowing my chances of survival were nonexistent I continued to run around hoping to atleast die in a good CR spot. Cussing at my computer screen and planning my next moves and selected tells for aid in CR ( im bound in nexus) Low and behold Lady Vox herself spawns on top of me and as expected summons me to zone in with 20 percent health. That was probably the single most intense moment of my EQ life. Im not a beting man but what are the Odds of Lady Vox spawning at that exact moment. I dare not think about it.<br>
<br>
